=Description=

"Open-Mesh creates ultra low-cost zero-config, plug & play wireless mesh network solutions that spread an Internet connection throughout a hotel, apartment, neighborhood, village, coffee shop, shopping mall, campground, marina and just about anywhere else you can imagine.

We provide all the components you need: routers, indoor wall-plug and outdoor housings and free hosted management / control software. You can set the bandwidth users get, design your own splash pages, and even easily add billing and user management options via several third-party solutions.

A typical network consists of 2 or more routers, one connected to your DSL or cable modem, and others plugged into outlets around the area you'd like to cover."


